commit.message: make h2o_fatal use h2o__fatal_redirect function pointer #3244

http3client: socket pool DNS resolution must only return addresses
corresponding to the address family of `st_h2o_quic_ctx_t`

Before this fix, if name resolution was used by the http3 client, it
might have returned a result that didn't correspond to the socket used
in `st_h2o_quic_ctx_t`.
